{
  "stem": "1581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at long last, we rolled into a station through a very strange gate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- no, it was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the train came to a stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now things happen which I-- which was very hard to believe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Doors were opened of the rig, and in came people in striped prisoner garb.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were obviously Jewish and Polish, and they started to yell and scream at us and push us out of the car.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Leave everything in the car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whoever had a watch on his hand, they tore it off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't need this anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you have anything, give it to me because we don't need it anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were just shocked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that time I didn't speak any Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I learned it only later in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my wife did, and she tried to talk to the people, but they didn't even react.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were roughly pushed out of the car, and we had to line up on this ramp next to the platform, next to the train.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had to align ourselves in fours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And slowly this column moved towards the end of the ramp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I saw the masses of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I saw on the end of the ramp there were four immaculately uniformed SS officers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of them was a stunningly beautiful man with gloves, and it was the famous and notorious Dr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mengele.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the rumor went around, and I knew of his-- I never knew of his existence, but later on somehow I knew who he was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was called the angel of death.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
